{
  "video_id": "6-eYu0fCtU8",
  "title": "How loss helped one artist find beauty in imperfection | Alyssa Monks",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 14120.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a painter."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14120.0,
      "end_time": 16720.0,
      "text": "I make large-scale figurative paintings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16720.0,
      "end_time": 18840.0,
      "text": "which means I paint people"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18840.0,
      "end_time": 20840.0,
      "text": "like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20840.0,
      "end_time": 23640.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m here tonight to tell you about something personal"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23640.0,
      "end_time": 27520.0,
      "text": "that changed my work and my perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27520.0,
      "end_time": 29240.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something we all go through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29240.0,
      "end_time": 34520.0,
      "text": "and my hope is that my experience may be helpful to somebody."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34520.0,
      "end_time": 38120.0,
      "text": "To give you some background on me, I grew up the youngest of eight."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38120.0,
      "end_time": 40320.0,
      "text": "Yes, eight kids in my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40320.0,
      "end_time": 42680.0,
      "text": "I have six older brothers and a sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42680.0,
      "end_time": 45720.0,
      "text": "To give you a sense of what that&#39;s like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45720.0,
      "end_time": 47760.0,
      "text": "when my family went on vacation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47760.0,
      "end_time": 49480.0,
      "text": "we had a bus."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49480.0,
      "end_time": 52920.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52920.0,
      "end_time": 55680.0,
      "text": "My supermom would drive us all over town"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55680.0,
      "end_time": 58440.0,
      "text": "to our various after-school activities --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58440.0,
      "end_time": 60920.0,
      "text": "not in the bus."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60920.0,
      "end_time": 63920.0,
      "text": "We had a regular car, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63920.0,
      "end_time": 65760.0,
      "text": "She would take me to art classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65760.0,
      "end_time": 67040.0,
      "text": "and not just one or two."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67040.0,
      "end_time": 72640.0,
      "text": "She took me to every available art class from when I was eight to 16,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72640.0,
      "end_time": 74760.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s all I wanted to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74760.0,
      "end_time": 78040.0,
      "text": "She even took a class with me in New York City."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78040.0,
      "end_time": 81760.0,
      "text": "Now, being the youngest of eight, I learned a few survival skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81760.0,
      "end_time": 83320.0,
      "text": "Rule number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83320.0,
      "end_time": 87600.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t let your big brother see you do anything stupid."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87600.0,
      "end_time": 90120.0,
      "text": "So I learned to be quiet and neat"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90120.0,
      "end_time": 93520.0,
      "text": "and careful to follow the rules and stay in line."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93520.0,
      "end_time": 96640.0,
      "text": "But painting was where I made the rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96640.0,
      "end_time": 99560.0,
      "text": "That was my private world."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99560.0,
      "end_time": 103880.0,
      "text": "By 14, I knew I really wanted to be an artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103880.0,
      "end_time": 108440.0,
      "text": "My big plan was to be a waitress to support my painting."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108440.0,
      "end_time": 110320.0,
      "text": "So I continued honing my skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110320.0,
      "end_time": 112480.0,
      "text": "I went to graduate school and I got an MFA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112480.0,
      "end_time": 115800.0,
      "text": "and at my first solo show, my brother asked me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115800.0,
      "end_time": 118800.0,
      "text": "&quot;What do all these red dots mean next to the paintings?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118800.0,
      "end_time": 121560.0,
      "text": "Nobody was more surprised than me."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121560.0,
      "end_time": 124040.0,
      "text": "The red dots meant that the paintings were sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124040.0,
      "end_time": 126160.0,
      "text": "and that I&#39;d be able to pay my rent"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 128040.0,
      "text": "with painting."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128039.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131400.0,
      "text": "Now, my apartment had four electrical outlets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131400.0,
      "end_time": 134720.0,
      "text": "and I couldn&#39;t use a microwave and a toaster at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134720.0,
      "end_time": 137480.0,
      "text": "but still, I could pay my rent."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137480.0,
      "end_time": 140000.0,
      "text": "So I was very happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140000.0,
      "end_time": 143400.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a painting from back around that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143400.0,
      "end_time": 145560.0,
      "text": "I needed it to be as realistic as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145560.0,
      "end_time": 149400.0,
      "text": "It had to be specific and believable."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149400.0,
      "end_time": 155680.0,
      "text": "This was the place where I was isolated and in total control."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155680.0,
      "end_time": 159400.0,
      "text": "Since then, I&#39;ve made a career of painting people in water."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159400.0,
      "end_time": 163440.0,
      "text": "Bathtubs and showers were the perfect enclosed environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163440.0,
      "end_time": 165200.0,
      "text": "It was intimate and private,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165200.0,
      "end_time": 169440.0,
      "text": "and water was this complicated challenge that kept me busy for a decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 169440.0,
      "end_time": 172000.0,
      "text": "I made about 200 of these paintings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172000.0,
      "end_time": 174440.0,
      "text": "some of them six to eight feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174440.0,
      "end_time": 176240.0,
      "text": "like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176240.0,
      "end_time": 180760.0,
      "text": "For this painting, I mixed flour in with the bathwater to make it cloudy"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 180760.0,
      "end_time": 183760.0,
      "text": "and I floated cooking oil on the surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183760.0,
      "end_time": 185120.0,
      "text": "and stuck a girl in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185120.0,
      "end_time": 186760.0,
      "text": "and when I lit it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186760.0,
      "end_time": 190080.0,
      "text": "it was so beautiful I couldn&#39;t wait to paint it."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190080.0,
      "end_time": 194560.0,
      "text": "I was driven by this kind of impulsive curiosity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194560.0,
      "end_time": 196520.0,
      "text": "always looking for something new to add:"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196520.0,
      "end_time": 199000.0,
      "text": "vinyl, steam, glass."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199000.0,
      "end_time": 202800.0,
      "text": "I once put all this Vaseline in my head and hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202800.0,
      "end_time": 205200.0,
      "text": "just to see what that would look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 205200.0,
      "end_time": 206440.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206440.0,
      "end_time": 210120.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210120.0,
      "end_time": 211840.0,
      "text": "So it was going well."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211840.0,
      "end_time": 213600.0,
      "text": "I was finding my way."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213600.0,
      "end_time": 215800.0,
      "text": "I was eager and motivated"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215800.0,
      "end_time": 217880.0,
      "text": "and surrounded by artists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217880.0,
      "end_time": 220320.0,
      "text": "always going to openings and events."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 220320.0,
      "end_time": 223240.0,
      "text": "I was having some success and recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 223240.0,
      "end_time": 228280.0,
      "text": "and I moved into an apartment with more than four outlets."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228280.0,
      "end_time": 230160.0,
      "text": "My mom and I would stay up very late"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230160.0,
      "end_time": 233320.0,
      "text": "talking about our latest ideas and inspiring each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 233320.0,
      "end_time": 236960.0,
      "text": "She made beautiful pottery."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236960.0,
      "end_time": 239440.0,
      "text": "I have a friend named Bo who made this painting"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239440.0,
      "end_time": 241840.0,
      "text": "of his wife and I dancing by the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241840.0,
      "end_time": 243960.0,
      "text": "and he called it &quot;The Light Years.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 243960.0,
      "end_time": 246600.0,
      "text": "I asked him what that meant, and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 246600.0,
      "end_time": 250960.0,
      "text": "&quot;Well, that&#39;s when you&#39;ve stepped into adulthood, you&#39;re no longer a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 250960.0,
      "end_time": 255000.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;re not yet weighed down by the responsibilities of life.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 255000.0,
      "end_time": 258560.0,
      "text": "That was it. It was the light years."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258560.0,
      "end_time": 260560.0,
      "text": "On October 8, 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 260560.0,
      "end_time": 262640.0,
      "text": "the light years came to an end."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262640.0,
      "end_time": 267160.0,
      "text": "My mom was diagnosed with lung cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 270680.0,
      "text": "It had spread to her bones, and it was in her brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270680.0,
      "end_time": 272959.0,
      "text": "When she told me this, I fell to my knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 272959.0,
      "end_time": 275720.0,
      "text": "I totally lost it."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275720.0,
      "end_time": 278160.0,
      "text": "And when I got myself together and I looked at her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 278160.0,
      "end_time": 279760.0,
      "text": "I realized, this isn&#39;t about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 279760.0,
      "end_time": 283000.0,
      "text": "This is about figuring out how to help her."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 283000.0,
      "end_time": 284440.0,
      "text": "My father is a doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284440.0,
      "end_time": 288040.0,
      "text": "and so we had a great advantage having him in charge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288040.0,
      "end_time": 290720.0,
      "text": "and he did a beautiful job taking care of her."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290720.0,
      "end_time": 293520.0,
      "text": "But I, too, wanted to do everything I could to help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 293520.0,
      "end_time": 296120.0,
      "text": "so I wanted to try everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 296120.0,
      "end_time": 297720.0,
      "text": "We all did."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 297720.0,
      "end_time": 299680.0,
      "text": "I researched alternative medicines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299680.0,
      "end_time": 303600.0,
      "text": "diets, juicing, acupuncture."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 303600.0,
      "end_time": 305000.0,
      "text": "Finally, I asked her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 305000.0,
      "end_time": 307280.0,
      "text": "&quot;Is this what you want me to do?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 307280.0,
      "end_time": 309360.0,
      "text": "And she said, &quot;No.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 309360.0,
      "end_time": 316160.0,
      "text": "She said, &quot;Pace yourself. I&#39;m going to need you later.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 316160.0,
      "end_time": 317920.0,
      "text": "She knew what was happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 317920.0,
      "end_time": 319360.0,
      "text": "and she knew what the doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 319360.0,
      "end_time": 321880.0,
      "text": "and the experts and the internet didn&#39;t know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 321880.0,
      "end_time": 324600.0,
      "text": "how she wanted to go through this."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 324600.0,
      "end_time": 327840.0,
      "text": "I just needed to ask her."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 327840.0,
      "end_time": 329960.0,
      "text": "I realized that if I tried to fix it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 329960.0,
      "end_time": 332440.0,
      "text": "I would miss it."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 332440.0,
      "end_time": 334080.0,
      "text": "So I just started to be with her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 334080.0,
      "end_time": 337400.0,
      "text": "whatever that meant and whatever situation came up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 337400.0,
      "end_time": 340320.0,
      "text": "just really listen to her."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 340320.0,
      "end_time": 345200.0,
      "text": "If before I was resisting, then now I was surrendering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 345200.0,
      "end_time": 347840.0,
      "text": "giving up trying to control the uncontrollable"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 347840.0,
      "end_time": 351760.0,
      "text": "and just being there in it with her."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 351760.0,
      "end_time": 353840.0,
      "text": "Time slowed down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 353840.0,
      "end_time": 357000.0,
      "text": "and the date was irrelevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 357000.0,
      "end_time": 359440.0,
      "text": "We developed a routine."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 359440.0,
      "end_time": 363160.0,
      "text": "Early each morning I would crawl into bed with her and sleep with her."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363160.0,
      "end_time": 364880.0,
      "text": "My brother would come for breakfast"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 364880.0,
      "end_time": 367680.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d be so glad to hear his car coming up the driveway."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 367680.0,
      "end_time": 371200.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d help her up and take both her hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 371200.0,
      "end_time": 373960.0,
      "text": "and help her walk to the kitchen."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 373960.0,
      "end_time": 377240.0,
      "text": "She had this huge mug she made"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377240.0,
      "end_time": 379800.0,
      "text": "she loved to drink her coffee out of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 379800.0,
      "end_time": 383600.0,
      "text": "and she loved Irish soda bread for breakfast."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 383600.0,
      "end_time": 385000.0,
      "text": "Afterwards was the shower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 385000.0,
      "end_time": 386280.0,
      "text": "and she loved this part."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 386280.0,
      "end_time": 387840.0,
      "text": "She loved the warm water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 387840.0,
      "end_time": 391320.0,
      "text": "so I made this as indulgent as I could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 391320.0,
      "end_time": 393360.0,
      "text": "like a spa."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 393360.0,
      "end_time": 395120.0,
      "text": "My sister would help sometimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 395120.0,
      "end_time": 397440.0,
      "text": "We had warm towels"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 397440.0,
      "end_time": 399600.0,
      "text": "and slippers ready immediately"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 399600.0,
      "end_time": 402920.0,
      "text": "so she never got cold for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 402920.0,
      "end_time": 405200.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d blow-dry her hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 405200.0,
      "end_time": 408080.0,
      "text": "My brothers would come in the evenings and bring their kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 408080.0,
      "end_time": 411080.0,
      "text": "and that was the highlight of her day."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 411080.0,
      "end_time": 414080.0,
      "text": "Over time, we started to use a wheelchair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 414080.0,
      "end_time": 415800.0,
      "text": "and she didn&#39;t want to eat so much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 415800.0,
      "end_time": 423120.0,
      "text": "and she used the tiniest little teacup we could find to drink her coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 423120.0,
      "end_time": 425000.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t support her myself anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 425000.0,
      "end_time": 428440.0,
      "text": "so we hired an aide to help me with the showers."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 428440.0,
      "end_time": 431080.0,
      "text": "These simple daily activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 431080.0,
      "end_time": 433920.0,
      "text": "became our sacred ritual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 433920.0,
      "end_time": 435760.0,
      "text": "and we repeated them day after day"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 435760.0,
      "end_time": 437560.0,
      "text": "as the cancer grew."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 437560.0,
      "end_time": 439720.0,
      "text": "It was humbling and painful"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 439720.0,
      "end_time": 444160.0,
      "text": "and exactly where I wanted to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 444160.0,
      "end_time": 448280.0,
      "text": "We called this time &quot;the beautiful awful.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448280.0,
      "end_time": 452000.0,
      "text": "She died on October 26, 2012."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 452000.0,
      "end_time": 456760.0,
      "text": "It was a year and three weeks after her diagnosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 456760.0,
      "end_time": 461520.0,
      "text": "She was gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 461520.0,
      "end_time": 463520.0,
      "text": "My brothers, sister, and father and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 463520.0,
      "end_time": 467903.0,
      "text": "all came together in this supportive and attentive way."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 467903.0,
      "end_time": 469880.0,
      "text": "It was as though our whole family dynamic"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 469880.0,
      "end_time": 471960.0,
      "text": "and all our established roles vanished"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 471960.0,
      "end_time": 474640.0,
      "text": "and we were just all together in this unknown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 474640.0,
      "end_time": 476520.0,
      "text": "feeling the same thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 476520.0,
      "end_time": 479640.0,
      "text": "and taking care of each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 479640.0,
      "end_time": 485160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m so grateful for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 485160.0,
      "end_time": 488800.0,
      "text": "As someone who spends most of my time alone in a studio working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 488800.0,
      "end_time": 491680.0,
      "text": "I had no idea that this kind of connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 491680.0,
      "end_time": 494640.0,
      "text": "could be so important, so healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 494640.0,
      "end_time": 498120.0,
      "text": "This was the most important thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498120.0,
      "end_time": 501160.0,
      "text": "It was what I always wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 501160.0,
      "end_time": 507600.0,
      "text": "So after the funeral, it was time for me to go back to my studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 507600.0,
      "end_time": 510440.0,
      "text": "So I packed up my car and I drove back to Brooklyn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 510440.0,
      "end_time": 514400.0,
      "text": "and painting is what I&#39;ve always done, so that&#39;s what I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 514400.0,
      "end_time": 519120.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 519120.0,
      "end_time": 525919.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like a release of everything that was unraveling in me."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 525919.0,
      "end_time": 530919.0,
      "text": "That safe, very, very carefully rendered safe place"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 530919.0,
      "end_time": 533880.0,
      "text": "that I created in all my other paintings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 533880.0,
      "end_time": 535159.0,
      "text": "it was a myth."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 535159.0,
      "end_time": 537280.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 537280.0,
      "end_time": 543120.0,
      "text": "And I was afraid, because I didn&#39;t want to paint anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 543120.0,
      "end_time": 544600.0,
      "text": "So I went into the woods."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 544600.0,
      "end_time": 548240.0,
      "text": "I thought, I&#39;ll try that, going outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 548240.0,
      "end_time": 552080.0,
      "text": "I got my paints, and I wasn&#39;t a landscape painter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 552080.0,
      "end_time": 554720.0,
      "text": "but I wasn&#39;t really much of any kind of painter at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 554720.0,
      "end_time": 557240.0,
      "text": "so I had no attachment, no expectation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 557240.0,
      "end_time": 560320.0,
      "text": "which allowed me to be reckless and free."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 560320.0,
      "end_time": 562400.0,
      "text": "I actually left one of these wet paintings"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 562400.0,
      "end_time": 565000.0,
      "text": "outside overnight"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 565000.0,
      "end_time": 568200.0,
      "text": "next to a light in the woods."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 568200.0,
      "end_time": 572520.0,
      "text": "By the morning it was lacquered with bugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 572520.0,
      "end_time": 575160.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t care. It didn&#39;t matter. It didn&#39;t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 575160.0,
      "end_time": 577560.0,
      "text": "I took all these paintings back to my studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 577560.0,
      "end_time": 580240.0,
      "text": "and scraped them, and carved into them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 580240.0,
      "end_time": 582760.0,
      "text": "and poured paint thinner on them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 582760.0,
      "end_time": 585080.0,
      "text": "put more paint on top, drew on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 585080.0,
      "end_time": 587320.0,
      "text": "I had no plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587320.0,
      "end_time": 590680.0,
      "text": "but I was watching what was happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 590680.0,
      "end_time": 593960.0,
      "text": "This is the one with all the bugs in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 593960.0,
      "end_time": 596120.0,
      "text": "I wasn&#39;t trying to represent a real space."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 596120.0,
      "end_time": 600600.0,
      "text": "It was the chaos and the imperfections that were fascinating me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 600600.0,
      "end_time": 603680.0,
      "text": "and something started to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 603680.0,
      "end_time": 606320.0,
      "text": "I got curious again."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 606320.0,
      "end_time": 610320.0,
      "text": "This is another one from the woods."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 610320.0,
      "end_time": 612160.0,
      "text": "There was a caveat now, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 612160.0,
      "end_time": 615120.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t be controlling the paint like I used to."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 615120.0,
      "end_time": 618160.0,
      "text": "It had to be about implying and suggesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 618160.0,
      "end_time": 621760.0,
      "text": "not explaining or describing."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 621760.0,
      "end_time": 626040.0,
      "text": "And that imperfect, chaotic, turbulent surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 626040.0,
      "end_time": 630240.0,
      "text": "is what told the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 630240.0,
      "end_time": 634000.0,
      "text": "I started to be as curious as I was when I was a student."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 634000.0,
      "end_time": 638120.0,
      "text": "So the next thing was I wanted to put figures in these paintings, people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 638120.0,
      "end_time": 639920.0,
      "text": "and I loved this new environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 639920.0,
      "end_time": 645760.0,
      "text": "so I wanted to have both people and this atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 645760.0,
      "end_time": 647920.0,
      "text": "When the idea hit me of how to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 647920.0,
      "end_time": 650720.0,
      "text": "I got kind of nauseous and dizzy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 650720.0,
      "end_time": 653600.0,
      "text": "which is really just adrenaline, probably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 653600.0,
      "end_time": 656560.0,
      "text": "but for me it&#39;s a really good sign."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 656560.0,
      "end_time": 659720.0,
      "text": "And so now I want to show you what I&#39;ve been working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 659720.0,
      "end_time": 663800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something I haven&#39;t shown yet, and it&#39;s like a preview, I guess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 663800.0,
      "end_time": 665080.0,
      "text": "of my upcoming show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 665080.0,
      "end_time": 668280.0,
      "text": "what I have so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 668280.0,
      "end_time": 671000.0,
      "text": "Expansive space"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 671000.0,
      "end_time": 673480.0,
      "text": "instead of the isolated bathtub."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 673480.0,
      "end_time": 677480.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going outside instead of inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 677480.0,
      "end_time": 679880.0,
      "text": "Loosening control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 679880.0,
      "end_time": 681920.0,
      "text": "savoring the imperfections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 681920.0,
      "end_time": 684160.0,
      "text": "allowing the --"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 684160.0,
      "end_time": 687680.0,
      "text": "allowing the imperfections."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 687680.0,
      "end_time": 689360.0,
      "text": "And in that imperfection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 689360.0,
      "end_time": 691280.0,
      "text": "you can find a vulnerability."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 691280.0,
      "end_time": 698000.0,
      "text": "I could feel my deepest intention, what matters most to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 698000.0,
      "end_time": 700400.0,
      "text": "that human connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 700400.0,
      "end_time": 705560.0,
      "text": "that can happen in a space where there&#39;s no resisting or controlling."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 705560.0,
      "end_time": 710280.0,
      "text": "I want to make paintings about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 710280.0,
      "end_time": 713240.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what I learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 713240.0,
      "end_time": 717000.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all going to have big losses in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 717000.0,
      "end_time": 719080.0,
      "text": "maybe a job or a career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 719080.0,
      "end_time": 723520.0,
      "text": "relationships, love, our youth."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 723520.0,
      "end_time": 725760.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to lose our health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 725760.0,
      "end_time": 728240.0,
      "text": "people we love."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 728240.0,
      "end_time": 730680.0,
      "text": "These kinds of losses are out of our control."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 730680.0,
      "end_time": 732720.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re unpredictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 732720.0,
      "end_time": 735520.0,
      "text": "and they bring us to our knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 735520.0,
      "end_time": 738840.0,
      "text": "And so I say, let them."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 738840.0,
      "end_time": 742920.0,
      "text": "Fall to your knees. Be humbled."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 742920.0,
      "end_time": 745280.0,
      "text": "Let go of trying to change it"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 745280.0,
      "end_time": 747440.0,
      "text": "or even wanting it to be different."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 747440.0,
      "end_time": 751160.0,
      "text": "It just is."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 751160.0,
      "end_time": 752640.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 752640.0,
      "end_time": 755840.0,
      "text": "and in that space feel your vulnerability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 755840.0,
      "end_time": 757560.0,
      "text": "what matters most to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 757560.0,
      "end_time": 760640.0,
      "text": "your deepest intention."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 760640.0,
      "end_time": 763600.0,
      "text": "And be curious to connect"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 763600.0,
      "end_time": 767440.0,
      "text": "to what and who is really here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 767440.0,
      "end_time": 770120.0,
      "text": "awake and alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 770120.0,
      "end_time": 772800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what we all want."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 772800.0,
      "end_time": 776720.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take the opportunity to find something beautiful"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 776720.0,
      "end_time": 780760.0,
      "text": "in the unknown, in the unpredictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 780760.0,
      "end_time": 783320.0,
      "text": "and even in the awful."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 783320.0,
      "end_time": 784560.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 784560.0,
      "end_time": 794560.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}